''See also [[Grace]], [[Graces]], [[grâce]]''
==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|grace|graces}}

#''(uncountable)'' [[elegant|Elegant]] [[movement]]; [[poise]] or [[balance]].
#''(uncountable)'' {{theology}}: Free and [[undeserve]]d [[favour]], especially of [[God]].
#''(countable)'' Short [[prayer]] of [[thank]]s before or after a [[meal]].
#:''It has become less common to say '''graces''' before having dinner.''

